            "body": "This is a nice report 👍 \n\n> Adding client filtering to `get_locations()` would be an alternative\n\n`on_list` exists for the purpose (as you noticed), though maybe it's not the most elegant.\n\n> deduplicated (by `filename:lnum:col`)\n\nbut the warning may not be the same, even if it's at the same location?\n\nIf there is a reliable way for `get_locations` to \"do the right thing\" then I think we'd be in favor of changing that internally.",
